419
00:40:42.125 --> 00:40:43.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anne?

420
00:40:52.250 --> 00:40:54.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
