421
00:40:54.583 --> 00:40:55.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Evet.</i>

422
00:40:55.583 --> 00:40:58.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Evet, Tryvann kulesinde. Dedi ki…</i>

423
00:41:00.041 --> 00:41:03.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ne düşünüyorsun Laurits?
Bunu giyebilir miyim?

424
00:41:04.166 --> 00:41:05.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Harika.

425
00:41:06.291 --> 00:41:08.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey. Bir gün sen de aşkını bulacaksın.

426
00:41:09.166 --> 00:41:10.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu tür şeyler zaman ister.

427
00:41:14.958 --> 00:41:16.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Odandaki o şeyi

428
00:41:16.916 --> 00:41:18.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
sevdiğini biliyorum

429
00:41:18.208 --> 00:41:20.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
fakat burada olamaz. Ondan kurtulmalısın.

430
00:41:20.916 --> 00:41:23.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Geç kaldım. Seni seviyorum.

431
