00:42:59.541 --> 00:43:01.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kim yaptı bunu?

438
00:43:02.666 --> 00:43:03.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sence kim?

439
00:43:07.833 --> 00:43:08.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Neden?

440
00:43:11.875 --> 00:43:13.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hain olduğum için.

441
00:43:16.375 --> 00:43:19.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ateşe ulaşman için Laurits'e
