443
00:43:26.583 --> 00:43:27.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Cezayı ben çektim.

444
00:43:54.333 --> 00:43:55.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Şu hâline bakıyorum da…</i>

445
00:43:59.000 --> 00:44:00.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
…ikimizin birlikte…

446
00:44:03.083 --> 00:44:06.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
…neler başarabileceğini
