447
00:44:11.750 --> 00:44:12.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Ciddiyim.</i>

448
00:44:14.375 --> 00:44:15.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Diğerleri salak.</i>

449
00:44:18.166 --> 00:44:20.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Kendi sonlarına neden olacaklar.</i>

450
