460
00:47:34.125 --> 00:47:35.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır…

461
00:47:35.791 --> 00:47:36.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu çok yanlış geliyor.

462
00:47:37.791 --> 00:47:42.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tecrübeyle alışırsın.
