475
00:48:27.500 --> 00:48:29.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>ve onu durdurmanızın yolu yok.</i>

476
00:48:29.708 --> 00:48:32.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayatımı bağışlarsanız sizi kurtarırım.

477
00:48:37.958 --> 00:48:41.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Onu öldürebilecek tek şey bende.

478
00:48:59.708 --> 00:49:02.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İşte orada. Gidelim buradan.

479
00:49:04.125 --> 00:49:05.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Blöf yapıyor.

480
00:49:07.666 --> 00:49:10.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
